<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Temporary Password - Heartly</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .password-box {
            background: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .password {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            font-family: monospace;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning strong {
            color: #856404;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #5a67d8;
        }
        .info-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîê Temporary Password</h1>
        <p>Your password has been reset by an administrator</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello,</h2>
        
        <p>Your password for your Heartly account has been reset by an administrator. Here are your temporary login credentials:</p>

        <div class="password-box">
            <h3>Temporary Password</h3>
            <div class="password">{{tempPassword}}</div>
            <p><small>This password is case-sensitive</small></p>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Information:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>This is a temporary password that expires on <strong>{{expiresAt}}</strong></li>
                <li>You must change this password on your first login</li>
                <li>Do not share this password with anyone</li>
                <li>This password can only be used once</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Reset Reason:</strong> {{reason}}
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Login to Heartly</a>
        </div>

        <h3>What to do next:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Click the "Login to Heartly" button above</li>
            <li>Use your email and the temporary password provided</li>
            <li>You'll be prompted to create a new secure password</li>
            <li>Choose a strong password that you haven't used before</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>üõ°Ô∏è Security Reminder:</strong>
            <p>If you didn't request this password reset or have concerns about your account security, please contact your facility administrator immediately.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent from Heartly - Healthcare Facility Management System</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Heartly. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>